column2: SELECT lcgID, ra, dec FROM MYDB.TESTE1 OPEN my_cursor WHILE (# = #) BEGIN FETCH NEXT from my_cursor into @lcgID, @ra, @dec IF (@@fetch_status < #) break INSERT MYDB.LCG_specObjIDs SELECT @lcgID, s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, n.distance FROM dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq (@ra, @dec, #) as n, SpecObjAll as s WHERE n.specObjID = s.specObjID END CLOSE my_cursor DEALLOCATE my_cursor
